description.plain:
Etre Un Homme Comme Vous , Is A French Cover Of “ I Wanna Be Like You ” From The 1967 Movie “ The Jungle Book” . Performed By Ben L'Oncle Soul , As A Track Of His 2013 Album “ WE LOVE DISNEY ” .
The Track Is Convo Between “ Mowgli the Man Cub ” & “ King Louie the Ape ” . This Convo Has Deep Meaning About Human Superiorty Among Species . Louie Asked Mowgli To Give Him The Secret To Make Fire “ The Light , Man’s Red Flower , The Power ” .
The Song Also Shows The Strength Of The Human Brain Versus The Physical Force .
